5. Core Service Offerings

A. Data Automation & Integration

Goal: Replace manual reports with dynamic data pipelines.
	•	ETL setup (SQL, Power Query, Zapier/Make)
	•	QuickBooks, Shopify, HubSpot, Stripe, etc. integrations
	•	Automated refresh schedules and validation

B. Analytics & Visualization

Goal: Deliver clarity through interactive, decision-grade dashboards.
	•	KPI dashboards for growth, revenue, and expenses
	•	Financial performance & variance monitoring
	•	Real-time trend analysis & anomaly detection
	•	Power BI / Google Data Studio builds

C. Financial Modeling & Strategy

Goal: Enable confident decision-making.
	•	Scenario-based models (runway, unit economics, breakeven)
	•	Cash flow forecasting and margin analysis
	•	Cost optimization modeling
	•	Investor and board-ready visualizations

D. AI-Driven Insights (Optional Add-On)

Goal: Automate commentary and highlight what matters.
	•	Monthly AI summary reports
	•	KPI trend explanations
	•	Outlier detection notifications







